  "texts": [
    "Additionally, I can relate to my mother's friend's experience, her name is Ayazhan.",
    "She has the electric car, Volkswagen Golf 8.Recently she had to go to Borovoye, a neighboring town located 256 km away.",
    "She went to the highway with a fully charged battery, but in the middle of the road her car had only 1% charge.",
    "The remaining 120 km she had to drive in cold weather without heating, music and her three children.",
    "With this example I want to show that our society is not ready for new technologies, also our ignorance about electric cars and their abilities plays a role.Consequently, the transition to electric vehicles instead of petrol or diesel vehicles requires several important points to be considered:1."
  ]
}